\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{H}$
\end_inset

施加了限制：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & H\left(x,0,0\right)=f^{q}\left(x\right)=q\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)-\bar{q}\left(-x\right)\theta\left(-x\right),\\
 & \tilde{H}\left(x,0,0\right)=\Delta f^{q}\left(x\right)=\Delta q\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)+\Delta\bar{q}\left(-x\right)\theta\left(-x\right),
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这里使用的
\begin_inset Formula $\left(f_{q},\Delta f_{q}\right)$
\end_inset

支持负数的动量分数。从这些约定中可以知道，对于chiral–even 和 parity–even 情形，反夸克分布满足
\begin_inset Formula $f^{q}\left(-x\right)=-\bar{q}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

，对于 odd 情形，
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta f^{q}\left(-x\right)=\Delta\bar{q}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

。对于 chiral odd 密度还有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\delta\bar{q}\left(x\right)=-\delta f^{q}\left(-x\right).
\]

\end_inset

对于GPDs 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{E}$
\end_inset

没有限制，由于当
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\to0$
\end_inset

时它们的狄拉克结构消失。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
胶子分布的定义为，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \bra{p}\mathcal{O}^{gg}\left(0,z^{-}\right)\ket{p}=\left(p^{+}\right)^{2}\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\left\{ e^{-ixp^{+}z^{-}}+e^{ixp^{+}z^{-}}\right\} xg\left(x\right),\\
 & \bra{p}\tilde{\mathcal{O}}^{gg}\left(0,z^{-}\right)\ket{p}=s^{+}p^{+}\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\left\{ e^{-ixp^{+}z^{-}}-e^{ixp^{+}z^{-}}\right\} x\Delta g\left(x\right),
\end{align*}

\end_inset

对于胶子GPDs有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & H^{g}\left(x,0,0\right)=xg\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)-xg\left(-x\right)\theta\left(-x\right),\\
 & \tilde{H}^{g}\left(x,0,0\right)=\Delta g\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)+x\Delta g\left(-x\right)\theta\left(-x\right),
\end{align*}

\end_inset

对于 maximal–helicity 胶子部分算符没有约化公式，由于
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{T}_{\mu\nu}^{g}$
\end_inset

在自旋
\begin_inset Formula $1/2$
\end_inset

强子态之间的向前矩阵元恒为零，由于夸克–强子螺旋度守恒。在 off–forward 情形，存在不为零的动量转移
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

，部分子存在非零轨道动量，所以存在
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{T}_{\mu\nu}^{g}$
\end_inset

部分的GPDs。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于非极化夸克分布，习惯上分成 valence 和 sea 夸克贡献。也就是对于非极化函数，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f^{q}\left(x\right)=q\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)-\bar{q}\left(-x\right)\theta\left(-x\right)=f^{q,\text{val}}\left(x\right)+f^{q,\text{sea}}\left(x\right),
\]

\end_inset

with
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & f^{q,\text{val}}\left(x\right)=q^{\text{val}}\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)\equiv\left\{ q\left(x\right)-\bar{q}\left(x\right)\right\} \theta\left(x\right),\\
 & f^{q,\text{sea}}\left(x\right)=\bar{q}\left(x\right)\theta\left(x\right)-\bar{q}\left(-x\right)\theta\left(-x\right).
\end{align*}

\end_inset

类似地，对计划情形也能定义 valence 和 sea 夸克分布
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta f^{q}\left(x\right)=\Delta f^{q,\text{val}}\left(x\right)+\Delta f^{q,\text{sea}}\left(x\right),
\]

\end_inset

with 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
